Let's do the experiments with the following configuration.

In our previous research, it has been frequently observed that

\begin{itemize}
  \item compensation for each frequency index
  \item compensation using the rectangular frequency response
  \item compensation using the gammatone-shape frequency response
\end{itemize}

The advantage of the rectangular frequency response over the
gammatone-shape frequency response is the rectangular frequency response
approach is simpler, and requires less computation for frequency domain


